headline: MGM, Venetian, Wynn and More Hotels Are Revving Up for the 2024 Las Vegas Grand Prix With Luxe Packages
summary: Ahead of the second annual Las Vegas Grand Prix, major hospitality and resort groups are going all-in to give their guests one-of-a-kind experiences throughout the race weekend.
